'''Tal'cara''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kothlis/Legends|Kothlis]]. It contained a [[Bothan Spynet/Legends|Spynet]] [[Bothan safe house|facility]]. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the [[Havocs]] [[Swoop gang/Legends|swoop gang]] sacked the city.

[[Maxeena Sov'lya]] was a local [[Crime lord/Legends|crime boss]] who ran protection rackets and smuggling in the city.<ref name="PSG">''[[Platt's Smugglers Guide]]''</ref>

{{City-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The ''[[Shadows of the Empire Planets Guide]]'' includes a city map of Tal'cara that is inexplicably titled "'''Kla'taal'''." However, the name Kla'taal is not mentioned anywhere else within the text or in any other source material. This article therefore treats Kla'taal as synonymous with Tal'cara, possibly as a working title that was not changed before the text's final publication.

